## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all cultural perspectives on happiness. Additionally, the complexity of measuring happiness and its biological impacts poses challenges, as happiness is a subjective experience influenced by numerous factors. Further research is needed to explore the causal mechanisms linking happiness and health across diverse cultural contexts.

